{"id":"api/common/http/provideHttpClient","title":"provideHttpClient","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/http\", \"name\": \"@angular/common/http\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/http/provideHttpClient\", \"name\": \"provideHttpClient\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common/http\">@angular/common/http</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/http/src/provider.ts#L77-L144\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"providehttpclient\">provideHttpClient<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient#providehttpclient\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2r2pz53g5nb874f924bo41ij0\">將 Angular 的 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClient</a></code> 服務設定為可注入。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a></span>(...features: <a href=\"api/common/http/HttpFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpFeature</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/common/http/HttpFeatureKind\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpFeatureKind</a>&gt;[]): <a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"38fwf35xy1ajri4niursk05yy\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>features</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpFeature</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/common/http/HttpFeatureKind\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpFeatureKind</a>&gt;[]</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withInterceptors\"><code>withInterceptors</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withInterceptorsFromDi\"><code>withInterceptorsFromDi</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withXsrfConfiguration\"><code>withXsrfConfiguration</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withNoXsrfProtection\"><code>withNoXsrfProtection</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withJsonpSupport\"><code>withJsonpSupport</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withRequestsMadeViaParent\"><code>withRequestsMadeViaParent</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withFetch\"><code>withFetch</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aasi9fjgunqto1fb7gqi4r08i\">預設情況下，<code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClient</a></code> 將設定為注入，其預設選項是對傳出請求的 XSRF 保護。可以透過將屬性函式傳遞給 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a></code> 來提供其他設定選項。例如，可以用 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/withInterceptors\" class=\"code-anchor\">withInterceptors</a>(...)</code> 屬性新增 HTTP 攔截器。</p>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ep666arkt8udyv7fi2drw9w7q\">強烈建議為使用伺服器端渲染的應用啟用\n<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API\"><code>fetch</code></a>以獲得更好的效能和相容性。要啟用\n<code>fetch</code>，請將\n<code><a href=\"api/common/http/withFetch\" class=\"code-anchor\">withFetch</a>()</code>屬性新增到應用程式根目錄下的\n<code><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a>()</code>呼叫中。</p>\n<code-example>\n<a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a>(<a href=\"api/common/http/withFetch\" class=\"code-anchor\">withFetch</a>());\n</code-example>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/http\n - api/common/http/HttpClientModule\n - api/common/http/HttpFeature\n - api/common/http/withInterceptors\n - api/common/http/withInterceptorsFromDi\n - api/common/http/withJsonpSupport\n - api/common/http/withNoXsrfProtection\n - api/common/http/withRequestsMadeViaParent\n - api/common/http/withXsrfConfiguration\n - api/core/APP_INITIALIZER\n - errors/NG02800\n - guide/testing-attribute-directives\n - guide/testing-components-scenarios\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/http\n - api/common/http/HttpClient\n - api/common/http/HttpFeature\n - api/common/http/HttpFeatureKind\n - api/common/http/provideHttpClient#description\n - api/common/http/provideHttpClient#providehttpclient\n - api/common/http/provideHttpClient#see-also\n - api/common/http/withFetch\n - api/common/http/withInterceptors\n - api/common/http/withInterceptorsFromDi\n - api/common/http/withJsonpSupport\n - api/common/http/withNoXsrfProtection\n - api/common/http/withRequestsMadeViaParent\n - api/common/http/withXsrfConfiguration\n - api/core/EnvironmentProviders\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/http/src/provider.ts#L77-L144\n-->"}